com.foreach.across.modules.logging.method

Class MethodLoggerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.logging.method.MethodLoggerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MethodLogger, org.springframework.core.Ordered

    public abstract class MethodLoggerAdapter
extends Object
implements MethodLogger, org.springframework.core.Ordered
    Base class to be implemented for a MethodLogger. Usually extended into an org.aspectj.lang.annotation.Aspect with the org.aspectj.lang.annotation.Around advice on proceedAndLogExecutionTime(ProceedingJoinPoint). The name of a logger must be unique.
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
